================================================================================
Third-party components
================================================================================

RWKV-LM and the RWKV-4-Pile-169M weights
  Upstream: https://github.com/BlinkDL/RWKV-LM
  Used:     The pretrained RWKV-4-Pile-169M model weights are baked into
            the Docker image and distributed unmodified. Inference uses
            the `rwkv` pip package from the same author, which provides
            the fast WKV CUDA kernel that our compression pipeline depends
            on.
  License:  Apache-2.0.

constriction
  Upstream: https://github.com/bamler-lab/constriction
  Used:     Range / ANS arithmetic coding of next-token distributions.
            Loaded via the `constriction` pip package.
  License:  MIT.

PyTorch + Hugging Face tokenizers
  Standard transitive Python dependencies of the inference path.
  Licenses: BSD-3-Clause (PyTorch), Apache-2.0 (tokenizers).
